title: Spotted: Suniel, Mana and Athiya Shetty at a fashion gala
text:
The Shettys -- Suniel, Mana and Athiya -- had a family outing for a charity fashion gala.

The event showcased designer clothes, jewellery, decor articles and other collectibles.
All proceedings from the fundraiser will be routed to educate less privileged, differently-abled children.
